1. Copy script from the following Github Gist link.
https://gist.github.com/Himanshu-Mish...â€‹


2. Create file in /usr/local/bin
[~] sudo vim /usr/local/bin/theme



3. Perform a search & replace to the file.


%s/org.pantheon.terminal.settings/io.elementary.terminal.settings/g

Basically, changing "org.pantheon.terminal.settings" with "io.elementary.terminal.settings"


4. Add execute permissions to the file.
[~] sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/theme


5. Run the theme command to run the script and select a pre-made theme. :)

